Metric: Customer LTV
Description: Lifetime paid revenue per customer with primary market context.
Owner: pipeline-builder
Tags: customers, ltv, ontology

Source: mart_customer_ltv

Given the customer exists in raw_customers
  And we sum revenue across all of their paid transactions

When we calculate
  Then sum the amount column for paid transactions
  And group by customer_id

The result is "Customer Lifetime Revenue"

Trust:
  Freshness must be less than 24 hours
  Null rate on customer_id must be 0%
  Row count must not drop more than 30% week over week
  Value must be between 0 and 100000
  Duplicate rate on customer_id must be 0%
